Token.Abstract: This protocol defines the method to be implemented to receive a call back when a user attempts login with a registered sign-in provider.
This method gets a call back to the assigned delegate when a user attempts login with a registered sign-in provider.

Parameter.Name: signInProvider
Parameter.Abstract: The instance of sign in provider implementing AWSSignInProvider protocol.

Parameter.Name: result
Parameter.Abstract: The result of login attempt. If error, set to nil.

Parameter.Name: error
Parameter.Abstract: The error if sign-in attempt failed. *
